                    "company": "Taller Ecologista",
                    "description": "As part of my research in the Delta del Paran\u00e1 for my Research MSc International Development Studies, I did my internship with the local Argentinian NGO Taller Ecologista. During my internship, I joined various meetings with the Wetlands Team. I also joined in various fieldworks in the wetlands as part of the NGO's project on indicators of sustainability for production in the wetlands. During these fieldwork trips we carried out interviews with local producers and isle\u00f1os (island dwellers) about their precarious land tenancy agreements and their livelihoods strategies. We furthermore carried out observations and experiments in order to obtain data that would help in understanding better the complex dynamics of production in a wetlands area, which would eventually aid in the development of indicators of sustainability.",
